511
00:22:33,766 --> 00:22:36,266
She said that she was sure you'd be making a wondrous song

512
00:22:36,266 --> 00:22:37,766
that will give everyone energy again!

513
00:22:37,766 --> 00:22:39,666
I'm no good anymore.

514
00:22:39,666 --> 00:22:42,566
I used to frequently say, "I'll possess you" or "I'll curse you",

515
00:22:42,566 --> 00:22:44,666
"but I never ever said "die".

516
00:22:44,666 --> 00:22:45,966
The only one who says something like that,

517
00:22:45,966 --> 00:22:48,266
is the monster that comes on in the Kamen Yaiba show.

518
00:22:50,866 --> 00:22:54,766
I've fallen low to that level.

