00:22:54,766 --> 00:22:55,866
But that's...

520
00:22:55,866 --> 00:22:58,966
Besides, after her letters stopped coming,

521
00:22:58,966 --> 00:23:00,466
I got to thinking.

522
00:23:00,466 --> 00:23:02,466
What did I do wrong,

523
00:23:02,466 --> 00:23:05,066
or what did she not like about me?

524
00:23:05,066 --> 00:23:08,166
When I started thinking this way, tears started pourings

525
00:23:08,166 --> 00:23:10,566
and I couldn't compose nor write lyrics.

526
00:23:10,566 --> 00:23:12,566
I couldn't write even a phrase.

527
00:23:12,566 --> 00:23:14,566
Phooey, talk about a fallen devil.

528
00:23:16,466 --> 00:23:18,766
Your tears are a bit red?

529
00:23:18,766 --> 00:23:21,766
That's President Urushibara's blood that splattered on him.

530
00:23:21,766 --> 00:23:22,766
Blood?

