00:23:54,466 --> 00:23:57,066
But it sure is like a fairy tale.

542
00:23:58,266 --> 00:24:00,666
Well, like they say,

543
00:24:00,666 --> 00:24:02,866
"When a devil sheds tears,

544
00:24:02,866 --> 00:24:05,366
he loses his evil powers".

545
00:25:36,966 --> 00:25:38,666
Now, something very shocking has happened!

546
00:25:38,666 --> 00:25:41,666
Ms. Kazuka Inoue, Yoko Okino and Azusa Yamamoto

547
00:25:41,666 --> 00:25:44,166
